name: When You Were Reading a Book
description:
It's always pleasing to see someone reading a book, and if what they read is a storybook. I always imagine they creating a new world with many acts and performances in their head, with various lighting. But this picture represents how much I miss reading storybooks. Still, the laziness always hit me up to preferably scrolling or reading on social media and maybe laying around daydreaming in my spare time.

Maybe this month I could finish a storybook.
